{"id": "1961", "post": "<div class=\"post-1961 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-lovevps-com tag-orlando tag-xen\" id=\"post-1961\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/lovevps-12quarter-128mb-xen-vps-in-orlando/\" rel=\"bookmark\">LoveVPS \u2013 $12/Quarter 128MB Xen VPS in Orlando</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/lovevps-com/\" rel=\"tag\">lovevps.com</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/orlando/\" rel=\"tag\">orlando</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xen/\" rel=\"tag\">xen</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> July 10, 2011 @ 10:46 am, by LowEndAdmin</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://www.lovevps.com/\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/images/lovevps2.jpg\" class=\"screenshot\" alt=\"LoveVPS\"></a> Matthew from <a href=\"http://www.lovevps.com/\"><b>LoveVPS</b></a> must have emailed me this <em>&gt; a month ago</em>. This is a follow up from their previous <a href=\"/blog/lovevps-7-512mb-xen-vps-in-scranton/\">Scranton 512MB Xen offer</a>. Matt mentioned that they have moved into a <b>more expensive</b> DC in Orlando, i.e. HostDime/DimeNOC. That means less profit margin, as they have kept the pricing the same. I do hope that they have kept the budget in check to avoid anything catastrophic :) Two offers:</p><ul><li>128MB memory</li><li>10GB storage</li><li>300GB/month data transfer</li><li><b>$12/Quarter</b> (<a href=\"http://my.lovevps.com/?cmd=cart&amp;action=add&amp;id=110\">Sign up link</a>)</li></ul><ul><li>512MB memory</li><li>20GB storage</li><li>500GB/month data transfer</li><li><b>$7/Month</b> (<a href=\"http://my.lovevps.com/?cmd=cart&amp;action=add&amp;id=106\">Sign up link</a>)</li></ul><p>Currently servers in Orlando are leased, but they will be moving some colo servers from BurstNET to HostDime. LoveVPS is founded by Matthew from UK in January 2011, <a href=\"/blog/lovevps-7-512mb-xen-vps-in-scranton/#comment-32949\">and got a praise from another Florida provider</a>. They had some hardware issue resulting downtime last month but has now planned some kind of DR solution to keep their site sync\u2019ed on two locations for fail-over.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Flovevps-12quarter-128mb-xen-vps-in-orlando%2F&amp;t=LoveVPS%20-%20%2412%2FQuarter%20128MB%20Xen%20VPS%20in%20Orlando\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=LoveVPS%20-%20%2412%2FQuarter%20128MB%20Xen%20VPS%20in%20Orlando&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Flovevps-12quarter-128mb-xen-vps-in-orlando%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https%3A%2F%2Flo